He spilled my change...

00:57:37.500 --> 00:57:38.648 line:85% position:50% size:80%
A beer, please.

00:57:46.250 --> 00:57:48.242 line:85% position:50% size:80%
A student ticket to Warsaw.

00:57:52.447 --> 00:57:53.510 line:85% position:50% size:80%
One to Łomża.

00:58:27.333 --> 00:58:30.974 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
Władek! Stop him!
Call the police!

00:58:44.708 --> 00:58:55.853 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
The only censored fragment
of the film lost beyond retrieval.

00:59:01.750 --> 00:59:04.442 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
- Name?
- Długosz. Witek Długosz.

00:59:04.791 --> 00:59:05.963 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Born?

00:59:06.048 --> 00:59:08.297 line:85% position:50% size:80%
June 27th, 1956. In Poznań.

00:59:09.625 --> 00:59:11.657 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
- Poznań?
- Yes.

00:59:12.875 --> 00:59:14.606 line:85% position:50% size:80%
You're a student?

00:59:14.833 --> 00:59:16.737 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Yes. On Dean's leave.

00:59:20.125 --> 00:59:22.414 line:85% position:50% size:80%
First, he got into a fight with me,

00:59:22.500 --> 00:59:25.726 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
then he beat a policeman
and tussled with my colleague.

00:59:26.916 --> 00:59:31.940 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
A week ago I caught him
urinating at the station.

00:59:32.958 --> 00:59:35.391 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
I didn't report it,
but that was him.

00:59:36.500 --> 00:59:39.217 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
- Is that true?
- No.

00:59:42.250 --> 00:59:49.510 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
We find the defendant guilty
and sentence him to thirty days

00:59:49.958 --> 00:59:54.826 line:85% position:50% size:80%
of supervised community work.

00:59:55.875 --> 00:59:57.039 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Kiss my ass.

00:59:57.125 --> 00:59:58.780 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
- Pardon me?
- Nothing.

00:59:59.208 --> 01:00:02.804 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
I hope the punishment will serve
its educational purpose.

01:00:41.541 --> 01:00:47.577 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
<i>In 1957, we're fourth-year university
</i><i>students. Twenty years from now...</i>

01:00:47.875 --> 01:00:50.447 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
- Got some wine?
- No, sorry.

01:00:52.170 --> 01:00:54.266 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
<i>Włodek will be
</i><i>a deputy Prime Minister,</i>

01:00:54.351 --> 01:00:55.891 line:85% position:50% size:80%
<i>Staszek - a minister,</i>

01:00:56.041 --> 01:00:57.717 line:85% position:50% size:80%
<i>Karol - an editor-in-chief.</i>

01:00:57.802 --> 01:01:01.690 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
<i>Jan will be abroad with an annual
</i><i>income of at least $100,000.</i>

01:01:02.375 --> 01:01:06.273 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
<i>We'll dig it out in April 1977.
</i><i>All signed.</i>

01:01:06.958 --> 01:01:10.206 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
Sons of bitches. They didn't
come to get it. It's May.

01:01:10.291 --> 01:01:12.442 line:85% position:50% size:80%
No last names, unfortunately.

01:01:12.958 --> 01:01:14.682 line:85% position:50% size:80%
What are you here for?

01:01:14.791 --> 01:01:18.472 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
A railroad guard picked a fight
with me. And you?

01:01:19.208 --> 01:01:20.818 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
- The FU.
- What?

01:01:21.750 --> 01:01:23.442 line:85% position:50% size:80%
The Flying University.

01:01:23.708 --> 01:01:26.789 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
I was making my apartment
available for lectures

01:01:26.875 --> 01:01:30.001 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
and a neighbor filed
a disturbance complaint.

01:01:31.458 --> 01:01:33.605 line:85% position:50% size:80%
What shall we do with this?

01:01:33.750 --> 01:01:38.195 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
We'll put it back. Maybe they'll
retrieve it from under the eagle.

01:01:38.625 --> 01:01:41.250 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
Any deputy Prime Ministers
named Włodek?

01:01:41.541 --> 01:01:42.641 line:85% position:50% size:80%
I don't know.

01:01:43.875 --> 01:01:46.105 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
Wait. Something's
on the other side.

01:01:46.958 --> 01:01:50.039 line:85% position:50% size:80%
<i>"I dug it up in 1975.</i>

01:01:50.125 --> 01:01:54.657 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
<i>Every night I thank God
</i><i>that you guys didn't make it. Jan."</i>

01:01:58.583 --> 01:01:59.771 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Marek.

01:02:01.125 --> 01:02:03.579 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
- Witek Długosz.
- No last names!

01:02:04.375 --> 01:02:05.530 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Why not?

01:02:06.541 --> 01:02:10.019 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
- Who told you all those things?
- My father.

01:02:12.500 --> 01:02:14.762 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Mine died two weeks ago.

01:02:16.208 --> 01:02:18.306 line:85% position:50% size:80%
I wasn't there.

01:02:20.416 --> 01:02:23.856 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
He told me over the phone
there was nothing I had to do.

01:02:24.251 --> 01:02:26.980 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
Then he gave me the same
message through a doctor we knew.

01:02:27.065 --> 01:02:28.744 line:85% position:50% size:80%
What did you have to do?

01:02:29.666 --> 01:02:33.630 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
He wanted me to be
a decent man, a doctor.

01:02:35.416 --> 01:02:37.304 line:85% position:50% size:80%
I don't know what he meant.

01:02:38.583 --> 01:02:41.231 line:85% position:50% size:80%
I'm told he didn't want to die.

01:02:42.583 --> 01:02:47.134 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
Though he seemed
resigned to his fate.

01:03:01.791 --> 01:03:02.949 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Hi.

01:03:03.375 --> 01:03:06.666 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
- Meet Stefan.
- Witek Dłu... Witek!

01:03:07.666 --> 01:03:09.650 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
- New?
- New and clean.

01:03:10.666 --> 01:03:11.844 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Here you go.

01:03:16.416 --> 01:03:18.923 line:85% position:50% size:80%
"The Worker" and other prints.

01:03:19.583 --> 01:03:23.219 line:85% position:50% size:80%
And 4000 for the books.

01:03:26.625 --> 01:03:30.755 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
Try to get something by Burek,
about literature,

01:03:31.083 --> 01:03:35.164 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
Górnicki's about the Church and Kowalik's
"Social System". Much sought after.

01:03:35.250 --> 01:03:38.155 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
Seven in total. Give it
to the free unions.

01:03:41.708 --> 01:03:43.581 line:85% position:50% size:80%
The phone number's inside.

01:03:43.666 --> 01:03:46.585 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Couldn't he deliver it?

01:03:47.458 --> 01:03:49.117 line:85% position:50% size:80%
He could, for starters.

01:03:49.291 --> 01:03:52.181 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
- Sure. Call and what?
- Arrange to meet.

01:03:52.541 --> 01:03:55.311 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
- Do I mention you, father?
- Call me Stefan.

01:03:55.833 --> 01:03:57.222 line:85% position:50% size:80%
It's hard, damn it...

01:04:04.250 --> 01:04:06.797 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
I was here a month ago.
I missed my train...

01:04:06.958 --> 01:04:09.483 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
If I hadn't, we wouldn't
have met.

01:04:10.458 --> 01:04:12.601 line:85% position:50% size:80%
It's not just blind chance.

01:04:13.041 --> 01:04:14.521 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Sometimes I think it is.

01:04:51.583 --> 01:04:53.905 line:85% position:50% size:80%
You forgot something, gentlemen?

01:04:54.916 --> 01:04:58.456 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
No. It's me.
I called yesterday.

01:05:07.791 --> 01:05:09.112 line:85% position:50% size:80%
What happened?

01:05:12.750 --> 01:05:16.327 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
- Did Stefan send you?
- The priest, yes. What happened?

01:05:17.958 --> 01:05:20.606 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Nothing happened.

01:05:27.750 --> 01:05:31.498 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
I have the money for you.
7,000.

01:05:32.708 --> 01:05:34.048 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Thank you.

01:05:34.291 --> 01:05:36.204 line:85% position:50% size:80%
I saw them... Bastards!

01:05:38.833 --> 01:05:41.476 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
Well, it's not
really their fault.

01:05:41.706 --> 01:05:44.302 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
It's not a big deal,
I'll clean up.

01:05:49.458 --> 01:05:51.596 line:85% position:50% size:80%
You've been with us long?

01:05:51.833 --> 01:05:53.108 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Not really.

01:05:54.125 --> 01:05:57.184 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
- You didn't know such things happen?
- I didn't.

01:06:00.208 --> 01:06:01.570 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Don't be ashamed.

01:06:01.958 --> 01:06:04.643 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
No need to be. Everyone's
ashamed.

01:06:07.990 --> 01:06:09.188 line:85% position:50% size:80%
I'll help you.

01:06:37.375 --> 01:06:39.137 line:85% position:50% size:80%
You dropped something.

01:06:42.625 --> 01:06:47.364 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
- So, what happened?
- They brought flowers.

01:06:49.125 --> 01:06:51.387 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
On behalf of the
workers, they said.

01:06:53.041 --> 01:07:00.268 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
Thanked me for helping those
who got fired or are oppressed.

01:07:01.500 --> 01:07:03.956 line:85% position:50% size:80%
And for anti-government leaflets.

01:07:04.041 --> 01:07:06.755 line:85% position:50% size:80%
It was really quite pleasant.

01:07:07.916 --> 01:07:10.347 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
I offered to make
some coffee.

01:07:10.541 --> 01:07:16.943 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
Suddenly, the tallest of them
grabbed the table and threw it over.

01:07:18.791 --> 01:07:20.748 line:85% position:50% size:80%
They were done in five minutes.

01:07:20.833 --> 01:07:22.186 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Weren't you scared?

01:07:23.625 --> 01:07:27.480 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
No. I'm living on
borrowed time.

01:07:29.833 --> 01:07:35.077 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
The surgery was to give me
three years. It's been twelve.

01:07:36.041 --> 01:07:40.286 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
If God gave me life,
I have nothing to fear.

01:07:41.166 --> 01:07:43.572 line:85% position:50% size:80%
I was scared. For a moment.

01:07:44.166 --> 01:07:47.748 line:85% position:50% size:80%
I didn't know it can get that bad.

01:07:47.833 --> 01:07:50.081 line:85% position:50% size:80%
I have nothing else to be scared of.

01:07:50.166 --> 01:07:51.300 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Good for you.

01:07:52.333 --> 01:07:56.668 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
- I have no one to worry about me.
- Same here.

01:07:57.291 --> 01:08:04.179 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
My parents and my husband are dead.
There's no one left to worry about.

01:08:06.875 --> 01:08:10.751 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
You really think it was God
who saved your life?

01:08:12.166 --> 01:08:14.630 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Who else could have?

01:08:17.417 --> 01:08:23.371 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
Trust me, He can come to you
if you do what He expects.

01:08:24.332 --> 01:08:27.484 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
If you help others,
He may come.

01:08:28.582 --> 01:08:33.375 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
Or try and invite Him yourself.
He'll understand.

01:08:40.957 --> 01:08:44.792 line:85% position:50% size:80%
They asked Mother Teresa

01:08:45.832 --> 01:08:49.974 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
what can you give a man
half an hour before his death?

01:08:51.582 --> 01:08:54.497 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
The faith that he's not
alone, she said.

01:08:56.375 --> 01:08:58.359 line:85% position:50% size:80%
I was alone for a while

01:08:58.542 --> 01:09:01.322 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
but you came
and I'm not any more.

01:09:02.625 --> 01:09:04.314 line:85% position:50% size:80%
I'm glad you came.

01:09:40.125 --> 01:09:41.949 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Are you looking for someone?

01:09:54.542 --> 01:09:56.537 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Witek, you're being followed.

01:09:57.792 --> 01:09:58.891 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Am I?

01:10:00.957 --> 01:10:02.270 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Not possible.

01:10:03.167 --> 01:10:05.747 line:85% position:50% size:80%
What exactly are you up to?

01:10:10.500 --> 01:10:14.789 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
<i>I don't like it, when they call me buddy,
</i><i>pat me on the shoulder with a grin,</i>

01:10:14.875 --> 01:10:19.430 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
<i>name me their "friend"or"brother",
</i><i>greet me with: "Hello, long time no see!"</i>

01:10:19.515 --> 01:10:24.082 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
<i>I don't like it, when they read my letters,
</i><i>look over my shoulder to take a peek.</i>

01:10:24.167 --> 01:10:29.153 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
<i>I hate those who gladly break one's
</i><i>face as a shortcut to saving the world.</i>

01:10:32.292 --> 01:10:36.707 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
<i>I detest the helpless expression
</i><i>of an animal shot at point blank range.</i>

01:10:36.792 --> 01:10:41.372 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
<i>I abhor the coincidental fashion which
</i><i>they use to block your road to change.</i>

01:10:41.457 --> 01:10:45.922 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
<i>I can't stand unaccountable reasons,
</i><i>irreparable losses make me sick.</i>

01:10:46.042 --> 01:10:50.792 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
<i>I hate counting unfulfilled wishes
</i><i>till the hangman hears the last I pick.</i>

01:10:54.625 --> 01:10:59.078 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
<i>I detest it when a crackling noise
</i><i>can be heard when I try to make a call.</i>

01:10:59.375 --> 01:11:04.037 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
<i>Shots in the back of someone's head
</i><i>are an abomination to me.</i>

01:11:04.292 --> 01:11:08.744 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
<i>I hate myself when I flinch,
</i><i>trying to excuse mean acts on my part,</i>

01:11:09.082 --> 01:11:13.664 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
<i>smile ingratiatingly at those I serve
</i><i>though I despise them with all my heart.</i>

01:11:13.984 --> 01:11:18.819 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
<i>Smile ingratiatingly at those I serve
</i><i>though I despise them with all my heart.</i>

01:11:21.542 --> 01:11:24.014 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
See you. To your right, OK?
You go left.

01:11:25.875 --> 01:11:28.164 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
Wait a moment...
OK, to your right.

01:11:28.250 --> 01:11:30.327 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
- See you in two weeks.
- Good!

01:11:32.250 --> 01:11:35.046 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Can I buy your record?

01:11:35.500 --> 01:11:36.845 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Sure. Over here.

01:11:37.500 --> 01:11:39.899 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
- Two please.
- Out and to your left.

01:11:45.582 --> 01:11:46.744 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Daniel?

01:11:47.832 --> 01:11:50.100 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
You don't recognize me?
To your right.

01:11:54.332 --> 01:11:55.524 line:85% position:50% size:80%
It's Witek!

01:11:56.000 --> 01:11:59.100 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
Summer of 1968. You were
leaving for Denmark.

01:12:00.707 --> 01:12:01.807 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Witek!

01:12:03.332 --> 01:12:04.516 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Hi!

01:12:06.707 --> 01:12:08.307 line:85% position:50% size:80%
My sister Wera.

01:12:09.662 --> 01:12:12.163 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
- You're back for good?
- No, just a few days.

01:12:12.248 --> 01:12:14.121 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Our mother passed away.

01:12:16.000 --> 01:12:17.400 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Relax. I'll check.

01:12:18.998 --> 01:12:20.109 line:85% position:50% size:80%
We'll stay, huh?

01:12:25.630 --> 01:12:27.207 line:85% position:50% size:80%
It's my apartment.

01:12:27.292 --> 01:12:32.039 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
If you do it again, I'll inform
the authorities.

01:12:36.582 --> 01:12:37.699 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Cigarette?

01:12:39.167 --> 01:12:42.250 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
- My aunt wants to call the police.
- Why?

01:12:43.207 --> 01:12:45.914 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
She's a pre-war communist,
a governor's widow.

01:12:46.000 --> 01:12:50.715 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
When we moved in
we had doors walled up,

01:12:51.332 --> 01:12:55.362 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
so it's a bit of a patchwork,
with stairs to the kitchen.

01:12:55.765 --> 01:12:56.832 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Will she call them?

01:12:56.917 --> 01:13:00.664 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
No, she's a good woman.
She thinks I'm being spiteful.

01:13:00.750 --> 01:13:04.078 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
And when she's really mad,
she addresses me as "comrade".

01:13:04.332 --> 01:13:08.118 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
- What are you smoking?
- "Sports". First thing I bought.

01:13:11.917 --> 01:13:15.719 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
She divorced our father
before we left and lived alone.

01:13:16.792 --> 01:13:19.717 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
Her neighbors were alarmed
by bottles of milk

01:13:19.802 --> 01:13:23.164 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
lined up on the doorstep
and discovered that she died.

01:13:23.250 --> 01:13:26.270 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
How's your father?
I only saw him briefly.

01:13:27.292 --> 01:13:29.788 line:85% position:50% size:80%
He builds highways in Denmark.

01:13:29.917 --> 01:13:32.140 line:85% position:50% size:80%
We have a house and all.

01:13:33.542 --> 01:13:35.747 line:85% position:50% size:80%
He got used to it, I can't.

01:13:35.832 --> 01:13:39.130 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
Can't get over the feeling
that I'm some place distant.

01:13:42.957 --> 01:13:44.599 line:85% position:50% size:80%
What does it mean?

01:13:45.542 --> 01:13:50.279 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
"I'm happy in this happy little
country." In Danish.

01:13:52.042 --> 01:13:53.895 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
Why didn't you
go with them?

01:13:55.375 --> 01:13:58.064 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
- I didn't want to.
- She fell in love.

01:13:58.500 --> 01:14:00.904 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
- Really?
- Yes.

01:14:01.625 --> 01:14:07.073 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
It was 1968. Someone yelled
"Jews go to Israel!" at her.

01:14:08.568 --> 01:14:11.600 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
A young man ran up
and punched that shouter in the face.

01:14:11.685 --> 01:14:15.685 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
She fell for him then and there.
He got expelled from the university

01:14:15.957 --> 01:14:21.095 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
and she ended up marrying him.
He's an aircraft engineer.

01:14:23.082 --> 01:14:26.649 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
Back then, I had no idea
why you had to leave.

01:14:28.457 --> 01:14:31.699 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
- How old were you, Wera?
- Eighteen.

01:14:32.207 --> 01:14:35.207 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
- And we were...?
- Twelve.

01:14:38.582 --> 01:14:41.756 line:85% position:50% size:80%
I remember us saying goodbye.

01:14:43.500 --> 01:14:48.645 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
Your father called you
to follow him uphill, to the car.

01:14:49.207 --> 01:14:50.694 line:85% position:50% size:80%
There was no car.

01:15:41.750 --> 01:15:45.230 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
- Will you come back to Łódź?
- Yes, I will. Soon.

01:15:47.207 --> 01:15:48.336 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Look for me.

01:16:25.375 --> 01:16:27.332 line:85% position:50% size:80%
You're here for a reason?

01:16:27.417 --> 01:16:29.341 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
- To get baptized.
- What?

01:16:33.707 --> 01:16:35.414 line:85% position:50% size:80%
I'd like to get baptized.

01:16:35.500 --> 01:16:38.185 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
Are you nuts?
Whatever for?

01:16:38.792 --> 01:16:40.842 line:85% position:50% size:80%
So I know what to live for.

01:16:41.332 --> 01:16:44.715 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
It brings reassurance
and peace of mind to so many people.

01:16:46.667 --> 01:16:48.105 line:85% position:50% size:80%
You, for example.

01:16:48.250 --> 01:16:51.845 line:85% position:50% size:80%
True. But you also need faith.

01:16:52.210 --> 01:16:54.476 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
I think I've it because
I know what to do.

01:16:54.561 --> 01:16:57.774 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
I want to voice my objections
instead of being passive.

01:16:58.167 --> 01:17:01.733 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
- Then join the Party.
- I won't find enlightenment there.

01:17:06.625 --> 01:17:07.809 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Do you pray?

01:17:08.917 --> 01:17:10.029 line:85% position:50% size:80%
No.

01:17:12.457 --> 01:17:14.796 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Try it sometime.

01:17:29.000 --> 01:17:30.180 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Oh Lord!

01:17:33.332 --> 01:17:36.579 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
It's done.
I've been baptized.

01:17:39.125 --> 01:17:40.296 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Here I am.

01:17:43.167 --> 01:17:45.417 line:85% position:50% size:80%
All the formalities are behind me.

01:17:47.750 --> 01:17:53.395 line:85% position:50% size:80%
And now I ask you... to be.

01:17:55.207 --> 01:17:57.497 line:85% position:50% size:80%
I'm ready, I'm baptized.

01:17:57.792 --> 01:18:00.001 line:85% position:50% size:80%
So please, don't fail to be.

01:18:01.457 --> 01:18:05.068 line:85% position:50% size:80%
I can't back out now.

01:18:05.332 --> 01:18:08.908 line:85% position:50% size:80%
I promise to never bother you again.

01:18:11.750 --> 01:18:12.969 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Just be.

01:18:16.207 --> 01:18:17.355 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Oh Lord...

01:18:24.750 --> 01:18:26.262 line:85% position:50% size:80%
998...

01:18:30.417 --> 01:18:31.565 line:85% position:50% size:80%
999...

01:18:37.582 --> 01:18:38.756 line:85% position:50% size:80%
1000.

01:18:39.332 --> 01:18:40.724 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Time for eggs!

01:18:43.082 --> 01:18:44.940 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
- How many do you want?
- Two.

01:18:46.332 --> 01:18:47.432 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Shorty!

01:18:51.417 --> 01:18:53.224 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Change of shift, wake up!

01:18:56.417 --> 01:18:58.961 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
- How many eggs you want?
- Three, please.

01:18:59.125 --> 01:19:00.427 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Or make it two.

01:19:16.137 --> 01:19:17.238 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Quiet!

01:19:18.417 --> 01:19:19.762 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
- Hi.
- Hi.

01:19:22.250 --> 01:19:26.449 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
- Got anything for me to take?
- We do, two thousand copies.

01:19:32.542 --> 01:19:33.720 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
- Hi!
- Hi.

01:19:37.667 --> 01:19:40.373 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
You haven't met? Shorty,
introduce yourself.

01:19:42.061 --> 01:19:45.055 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
Staszek is the son of my Dean
at the Medical Academy.

01:19:45.140 --> 01:19:46.130 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Marek.

01:19:46.542 --> 01:19:49.456 line:85% position:50% size:80%
I brought you something to read.

01:19:52.417 --> 01:19:55.546 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
- How about something normal to eat?
- I got eggs.

01:19:56.332 --> 01:19:57.478 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Gee...

01:19:58.832 --> 01:19:59.969 line:85% position:50% size:80%
What is that?

01:20:00.332 --> 01:20:02.680 line:85% position:50% size:80%
The Polish Independence Agreement.

01:20:13.167 --> 01:20:17.408 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
- Here's your passport. Got a visa?
- Yes. And a flight reservation.

01:20:19.042 --> 01:20:21.846 line:85% position:50% size:80%
What's the purpose of your trip?

01:20:22.250 --> 01:20:26.515 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
A Catholic youth rally outside Paris.
An international event.

01:20:26.875 --> 01:20:30.287 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
Your passport is ready, but it's not
as simple as that.

01:20:30.707 --> 01:20:32.920 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
You were in contact
with various people,

01:20:33.005 --> 01:20:35.912 line:85% position:50% size:80%
got arrested for illegal prints,

01:20:36.750 --> 01:20:41.240 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
- organized meetings at your apartment...
- I only made it available.

01:20:42.457 --> 01:20:43.578 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Never mind.

01:20:44.332 --> 01:20:47.819 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
We don't want you
to tell on your friends.

01:20:48.292 --> 01:20:49.501 line:85% position:50% size:80%
We know enough.

01:20:50.582 --> 01:20:55.454 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
But you'll meet
new people in France

01:20:56.000 --> 01:20:58.567 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
and we want to know
who they are.

01:20:59.332 --> 01:21:01.070 line:85% position:50% size:80%
And what's going on.

01:21:01.582 --> 01:21:05.194 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
We'll provide a phone number
and you'll call with the names.

01:21:07.042 --> 01:21:13.010 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
We can even narrow it down
to French citizens.

01:21:13.582 --> 01:21:15.042 line:85% position:50% size:80%
And if I agree?

01:21:17.292 --> 01:21:19.252 line:85% position:50% size:80%
You'll get your passport.

01:21:39.542 --> 01:21:41.609 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
Watch out.
He almost hit you.

01:21:55.957 --> 01:21:58.587 line:85% position:50% size:80%
I saved her from being run over.

01:21:58.957 --> 01:22:00.738 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
- I hadn't noticed.
- Come.

01:22:08.082 --> 01:22:09.974 line:85% position:50% size:80%
What a strange day.

01:22:12.417 --> 01:22:13.894 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Unlike any other.

01:22:15.292 --> 01:22:16.550 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Why?

01:22:17.250 --> 01:22:18.703 line:85% position:50% size:80%
I visited my mother.

01:22:20.792 --> 01:22:21.891 line:85% position:50% size:80%
And?

01:22:22.832 --> 01:22:26.195 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
Nothing. I visited her grave.
I have a grave to visit now.

01:22:26.457 --> 01:22:29.511 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Like everybody else.

01:22:31.457 --> 01:22:33.332 line:85% position:50% size:80%
I didn't have one before.

01:22:34.582 --> 01:22:36.387 line:85% position:50% size:80%
I came from nowhere.

01:22:36.625 --> 01:22:39.440 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
You don't understand
what it's like, do you?

01:22:40.207 --> 01:22:42.529 line:85% position:50% size:80%
It's all in your imagination.

01:22:43.875 --> 01:22:44.988 line:85% position:50% size:80%
No.

01:22:47.250 --> 01:22:50.317 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
You must have had
a grandpa, a grandma...

01:22:51.167 --> 01:22:54.197 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
Everyone has them.
You must have ancestors.

01:22:54.875 --> 01:22:56.524 line:85% position:50% size:80%
I know nothing about them.

01:22:58.369 --> 01:23:03.572 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
My mother never told me.
Then it was too late to ask.

01:23:05.210 --> 01:23:07.738 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
I don't know who they were,
where they are.

01:23:07.824 --> 01:23:09.150 line:85% position:50% size:80%
I know nothing.

01:23:09.417 --> 01:23:13.518 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
Two of my great-grandfathers
fought in the 1863 uprising.

01:23:14.667 --> 01:23:18.733 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
One grandfather fought
the Soviets in 1920.

01:23:19.417 --> 01:23:22.103 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Father fought in 1939,

01:23:22.375 --> 01:23:25.956 line:85% position:50% size:80%
and in workers' protests in 1956...

01:23:27.707 --> 01:23:29.934 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
He died in his bed
three years ago.

01:23:30.750 --> 01:23:32.557 line:85% position:50% size:80%
You have them all close by.

01:23:34.582 --> 01:23:36.153 line:85% position:50% size:80%
I never thought of that.

01:23:37.750 --> 01:23:40.664 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
What did your father tell you
when he was dying?

01:23:40.750 --> 01:23:42.288 line:85% position:50% size:80%
How do you know?

01:23:44.409 --> 01:23:49.869 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
He wanted to tell me something
but kept putting it off.

01:23:51.042 --> 01:23:54.957 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
I would call him repeatedly
to make sure he was alive.

01:23:55.042 --> 01:24:01.457 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
He'd been dying for months.
I'd hang up when he answered.

01:24:01.984 --> 01:24:04.225 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
So as not to constantly ask
how he was.

01:24:04.310 --> 01:24:06.918 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
He knew it was me
and why I was calling.

01:24:08.457 --> 01:24:09.703 line:85% position:50% size:80%
The tea is good.

01:24:10.875 --> 01:24:13.289 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
In my fourth year,
during an autopsy,

01:24:13.375 --> 01:24:16.755 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
a student had a funny look
on her face.

01:24:17.917 --> 01:24:20.470 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
They were cutting
up her teacher.

01:24:20.556 --> 01:24:22.220 line:85% position:50% size:80%
One she hated.

01:24:24.332 --> 01:24:29.163 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
She told me she fantasized
about doing it herself.

01:24:33.457 --> 01:24:35.243 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Why am I telling you this?

01:24:35.625 --> 01:24:39.113 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
Because I told you the plot
of the movie "Manhattan".

01:24:45.125 --> 01:24:50.378 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
We've been talking for so long
there must be nothing left to say.

01:24:52.125 --> 01:24:53.320 line:85% position:50% size:80%
I don't think so.

01:24:54.957 --> 01:24:57.945 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
There are many things
you can't tell anyone.

01:25:00.207 --> 01:25:02.006 line:85% position:50% size:80%
You have such things?

01:25:03.500 --> 01:25:04.622 line:85% position:50% size:80%
I do.

01:25:05.875 --> 01:25:07.957 line:85% position:50% size:80%
And you wouldn't tell me?

01:25:08.500 --> 01:25:09.693 line:85% position:50% size:80%
I wouldn't.

01:25:13.875 --> 01:25:15.810 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
- About fear?
- Yes.

01:25:16.042 --> 01:25:17.177 line:85% position:50% size:80%
What else?

01:25:20.707 --> 01:25:23.233 line:85% position:50% size:80%
A few things about my father...

01:25:23.653 --> 01:25:24.756 line:85% position:50% size:80%
About God...

01:25:24.841 --> 01:25:26.103 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
- God?
- God.

01:25:28.667 --> 01:25:30.355 line:85% position:50% size:80%
About my crooked toe...

01:25:33.832 --> 01:25:37.095 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
And there's something
I wouldn't know how to tell you.

01:25:38.332 --> 01:25:40.229 line:85% position:50% size:80%
But you would like to or not?

01:25:40.362 --> 01:25:44.889 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
I couldn't. Something about you,
and perhaps about me.

01:25:50.957 --> 01:25:52.243 line:85% position:50% size:80%
You're sleepy?

01:25:54.832 --> 01:25:55.949 line:85% position:50% size:80%
No.

01:25:57.336 --> 01:25:59.274 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Get up, I'll show you something.

01:25:59.917 --> 01:26:02.177 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
- I'm cold.
- Just a moment.

01:26:10.417 --> 01:26:11.564 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Found it.

01:26:12.042 --> 01:26:14.032 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Is this what we came to see?

01:26:18.582 --> 01:26:20.384 line:85% position:50% size:80%
There was a note inside.

01:26:20.667 --> 01:26:24.867 line:85% position:50% size:80%
From the past, about the future.

01:26:26.625 --> 01:26:29.393 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
And how it all turned out.
But it's gone now.

01:26:30.625 --> 01:26:32.354 line:85% position:50% size:80%
You were to go to France.

01:26:33.500 --> 01:26:35.783 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
I won't. I didn't get
the passport.

01:26:35.917 --> 01:26:39.083 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
It was to be my first
international flight.

01:26:39.667 --> 01:26:43.293 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
My husband works on
international flights. I always...

01:26:44.917 --> 01:26:46.573 line:85% position:50% size:80%
You told me before.

01:26:48.792 --> 01:26:51.354 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
You didn't want
to sleep with me...

01:26:52.082 --> 01:26:53.213 line:85% position:50% size:80%
I did.

01:27:30.875 --> 01:27:33.233 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
- Do you believe in God?
- I do.

01:27:37.042 --> 01:27:39.338 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
- Really?
- Yes.

01:27:45.167 --> 01:27:47.671 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
- Were you baptized?
- Recently.

01:27:52.082 --> 01:27:53.292 line:85% position:50% size:80%
What's it like?

01:27:54.082 --> 01:27:57.822 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
The priest asks if you want to
accept the Catholic faith.

01:27:59.832 --> 01:28:01.975 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
- And what do you say?
- That I do.

01:28:17.832 --> 01:28:18.935 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Witek!

01:28:20.375 --> 01:28:21.528 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Witek!

01:30:32.207 --> 01:30:33.409 line:85% position:50% size:80%
A giveaway?

01:30:34.750 --> 01:30:36.317 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Where were you?

01:30:37.500 --> 01:30:38.813 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Where are the guys?

01:30:41.332 --> 01:30:42.480 line:85% position:50% size:80%
In jail.

01:30:48.832 --> 01:30:52.177 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
You were supposed to be here.
Where were you?

01:30:53.582 --> 01:30:55.162 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Are you suspecting me?

01:30:55.417 --> 01:30:56.555 line:85% position:50% size:80%
The key.

01:31:01.792 --> 01:31:04.457 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
- And don't ever come here again.
- Man... Fuck!

01:31:04.542 --> 01:31:05.775 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Get the fuck out!

01:31:20.917 --> 01:31:22.462 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
No, I won't!
Don't you get it?

01:31:22.548 --> 01:31:25.497 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
Then wait. Things will
clear up.

01:31:25.667 --> 01:31:26.676 line:85% position:50% size:80%
What about me?

01:31:26.761 --> 01:31:33.329 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
Pray, so that you won't come
to hate those who accused you.

01:31:36.207 --> 01:31:39.452 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
And always remember
that this is a conspiracy.

01:31:41.292 --> 01:31:43.134 line:85% position:50% size:80%
The responsibility is twofold.

01:31:44.000 --> 01:31:45.872 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
Suspicion is hard
to shake off.

01:31:51.750 --> 01:31:57.252 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
You'll come to France with us.
We'll have plenty of time there.

01:32:04.707 --> 01:32:07.341 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
- You will calm down.
- I'm not going.

01:32:16.375 --> 01:32:17.981 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
Excuse me,
northbound buses?

01:32:18.127 --> 01:32:20.185 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
- Over there.
- Thank you.

01:32:40.000 --> 01:32:40.935 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Yes?

01:32:42.332 --> 01:32:45.216 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
- Is Wera home?
- No, she's not.

01:32:46.250 --> 01:32:48.868 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
- When will she be back?
- I don't know.

01:32:49.125 --> 01:32:51.087 line:85% position:50% size:80%
I'm a friend of her brother's.

01:32:52.750 --> 01:32:54.274 line:85% position:50% size:80%
She went to Łódź.

01:33:28.625 --> 01:33:34.569 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
I came to see you but you
weren't here. Waited four hours, Wera.

01:33:43.957 --> 01:33:45.902 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
- Did you hear?
- Hear what?

01:33:46.332 --> 01:33:47.554 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Wait.

01:33:49.750 --> 01:33:53.923 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
That girl who stayed with you
for a few days. Was she Jewish?

01:33:54.332 --> 01:33:55.442 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Yes.

01:33:55.957 --> 01:33:59.064 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
Many Jews were
great communists.

01:34:00.167 --> 01:34:01.338 line:85% position:50% size:80%
I know.

01:34:02.042 --> 01:34:03.905 line:85% position:50% size:80%
What are you listening to?

01:34:04.082 --> 01:34:05.207 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Free Europe.

01:34:05.293 --> 01:34:08.751 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
<i>Today, strikes began
</i><i>in a number of Polish cities.</i>

01:34:08.837 --> 01:34:11.863 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
<i>Workers at the URSUS tractor
</i><i>factory are protesting...</i>

01:34:11.948 --> 01:34:15.636 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
It's a good thing you haven't
left the country right now.

01:34:18.871 --> 01:34:23.088 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
<i>The train to Warsaw East Station
</i><i>will depart from Platform 2.</i>

01:34:27.917 --> 01:34:28.957 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Are you blind?

01:34:29.042 --> 01:34:31.434 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
- You'll break your neck!
- Sorry!

01:34:32.417 --> 01:34:34.025 line:85% position:50% size:80%
He spilled my change.

01:34:35.457 --> 01:34:36.641 line:85% position:50% size:80%
A beer, please.

01:34:41.582 --> 01:34:43.650 line:85% position:50% size:80%
A student ticket to Warsaw.

01:34:47.752 --> 01:34:48.853 line:85% position:50% size:80%
One to Łomża.

01:35:44.207 --> 01:35:45.770 line:85% position:50% size:80%
What are you doing here?

01:35:46.750 --> 01:35:50.074 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
I called you. Your aunt said
you were leaving.

01:35:50.832 --> 01:35:55.046 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
- I wanted to see you off.
- I missed it by five seconds.

01:35:56.625 --> 01:35:59.190 line:85% position:50% size:80%
I looked for you after the funeral.

01:36:09.667 --> 01:36:13.863 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
Remember our first time? On the floor
in the Students' Union room.

01:37:19.375 --> 01:37:21.619 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
I won't be signing
anything now.

01:37:25.957 --> 01:37:30.832 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
Leave your credit books
in my office. I have to go.

01:37:41.917 --> 01:37:43.283 line:85% position:50% size:80%
You're here to see me?

01:37:45.167 --> 01:37:47.679 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
Yes. I just don't know
how to begin.

01:37:48.167 --> 01:37:49.421 line:85% position:50% size:80%
I'm listening.

01:37:50.207 --> 01:37:52.158 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
You approved my
Dean's leave.

01:37:53.417 --> 01:37:57.094 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
Yes, I remember.
Is there something wrong?

01:37:58.042 --> 01:38:01.810 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
I'd like to come back.
I'll catch up.

01:38:02.332 --> 01:38:04.548 line:85% position:50% size:80%
I thought about it and...

01:38:04.750 --> 01:38:07.182 line:85% position:50% size:80%
You said you lost your calling.

01:38:07.375 --> 01:38:09.070 line:85% position:50% size:80%
It came back.

01:38:10.917 --> 01:38:12.926 line:85% position:50% size:80%
It doesn't show, I'm afraid.

01:38:13.792 --> 01:38:14.983 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Although...

01:38:26.917 --> 01:38:28.033 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Yes?

01:38:28.167 --> 01:38:30.292 line:85% position:50% size:80%
I have to tell you something.

01:38:31.042 --> 01:38:32.153 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Yes?

01:38:33.707 --> 01:38:35.478 line:85% position:50% size:80%
I'm three months pregnant.

01:38:55.917 --> 01:39:00.270 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
- You really want to marry me?
- I do.

01:39:01.250 --> 01:39:04.664 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
- Aware of the rights and duties
- Aware of the rights and duties

01:39:04.750 --> 01:39:08.957 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
- that result from starting a family
- that result from starting a family

01:39:09.042 --> 01:39:12.118 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
- I solemnly declare
- I solemnly declare

01:39:12.542 --> 01:39:16.689 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
- that I take Olga Matwiszyn
- that I take Olga Matwiszyn

01:39:16.957 --> 01:39:20.622 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
- to be my lawful wedded wife.
- to be my lawful wedded wife.

01:39:21.235 --> 01:39:23.238 line:85% position:50% size:80%
GRADUATION 1978

01:39:38.167 --> 01:39:40.609 line:85% position:50% size:80%
I wanted to talk to you.

01:39:41.667 --> 01:39:45.925 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
I'd like to offer you
an academic position.

01:39:47.167 --> 01:39:50.805 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
I wanted to work at a hospital
or at the ambulance service.

01:39:51.375 --> 01:39:55.972 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
Why not? We won't keep
you very busy here.

01:39:56.057 --> 01:39:59.009 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
You can complete specialty training,
get your M.D.

01:40:00.707 --> 01:40:02.789 line:85% position:50% size:80%
I've been almost too lucky lately.

01:40:03.125 --> 01:40:05.605 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
- Does it worry you?
- No.

01:41:39.250 --> 01:41:43.115 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
- Here are the prescriptions.
- Can't she be placed somewhere?

01:41:44.292 --> 01:41:47.180 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
I'll bring the medicines.
Come with me, please.

01:41:53.375 --> 01:41:58.225 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
I'll come by every few days.
Just don't give her up, OK?

01:41:58.582 --> 01:42:01.438 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
It won't be long now.
A month or two.

01:42:03.500 --> 01:42:04.948 line:85% position:50% size:80%
What are they doing?

01:42:05.917 --> 01:42:08.769 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
Practicing. They have been
for ten years now.

01:42:14.292 --> 01:42:15.579 line:85% position:50% size:80%
What for?

01:42:15.917 --> 01:42:20.729 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
Nothing. They say no one else
can throw so many balls at once.

01:42:40.625 --> 01:42:43.664 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
- Who talked to you?
- The first secretary.

01:42:43.750 --> 01:42:46.311 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
And another guy,
I don't know him.

01:42:48.875 --> 01:42:52.082 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
They promised to give me
an assistant position

01:42:52.167 --> 01:42:53.912 line:85% position:50% size:80%
and to fast track my M.D.

01:42:54.417 --> 01:42:57.033 line:85% position:50% size:80%
They did, didn't they? And?

01:42:59.042 --> 01:43:01.806 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
I don't want it. But how do I
tell them?

01:43:02.625 --> 01:43:05.354 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
- Do you believe in God?
- No.

01:43:06.863 --> 01:43:10.061 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
That doesn't matter.
Tell them that you do

01:43:10.146 --> 01:43:13.164 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
and that your worldview
couldn't accommodate both.

01:43:13.250 --> 01:43:15.271 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Yeah... They can't read my mind.

01:43:16.500 --> 01:43:20.537 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
When I had such visitors, I would say
I didn't believe in the Party.

01:43:21.417 --> 01:43:23.247 line:85% position:50% size:80%
But don't tell them that.

01:43:23.332 --> 01:43:24.970 line:85% position:50% size:80%
It always made them angry.

01:43:26.707 --> 01:43:29.042 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
But why won't you
accept their offer?

01:43:29.832 --> 01:43:31.042 line:85% position:50% size:80%
They're right.

01:43:31.957 --> 01:43:34.282 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
Life is much easier
for Party members.

01:43:34.750 --> 01:43:37.105 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
What they're doing
is an abomination.

01:43:37.625 --> 01:43:38.802 line:85% position:50% size:80%
No. I don't want to.

01:43:42.792 --> 01:43:44.742 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
You've got
milk whiskers.

01:44:07.457 --> 01:44:10.384 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
- I hear you got an offer.
- How do you know?

01:44:11.500 --> 01:44:13.927 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
From the hospital.
They say you refused.

01:44:24.792 --> 01:44:27.384 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
You want me to sing it
every night in bed?

01:44:28.875 --> 01:44:31.851 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
We've been administering it
for a week.

01:44:32.417 --> 01:44:34.179 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Any improvement?

01:44:34.375 --> 01:44:36.943 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
Here's his previous
ECG to compare.

01:44:40.375 --> 01:44:41.524 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Doctor...

01:44:43.875 --> 01:44:46.613 line:85% position:50% size:80%
The heart rate has slowed down...

01:44:47.332 --> 01:44:49.992 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
- Yes?
- Can you spare a few minutes?

01:44:51.792 --> 01:44:52.962 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Excuse me.

01:44:55.367 --> 01:44:57.203 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Can you see the difference?

01:45:08.000 --> 01:45:10.094 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
- Good morning.
- Hi. What is it?

01:45:11.417 --> 01:45:14.287 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
We're collecting signatures
from academics.

01:45:14.595 --> 01:45:15.706 line:85% position:50% size:80%
For what?

01:45:15.792 --> 01:45:17.899 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Students are given a hard time

01:45:17.984 --> 01:45:21.752 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
for distributing pamphlets
and for the Flying University.

01:45:22.582 --> 01:45:23.832 line:85% position:50% size:80%
This one. Who's he?

01:45:23.917 --> 01:45:27.390 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
They want to expel him.
For distribution.

01:45:27.520 --> 01:45:29.356 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
- But who is he?
- Our Dean's son.

01:45:29.442 --> 01:45:31.730 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
That's why the Dean
didn't sign.

01:45:37.082 --> 01:45:39.997 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
Rumor has it you refused
to join the Party.

01:45:40.082 --> 01:45:43.404 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
- I did, but I won't sign this either.
- Why not?

01:45:44.250 --> 01:45:47.060 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
I don't want to get involved
on either side.

01:45:47.832 --> 01:45:49.555 line:85% position:50% size:80%
It's only human to be scared.

01:45:50.028 --> 01:45:51.039 line:85% position:50% size:80%
I'm not scared.

01:45:51.125 --> 01:45:54.664 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
I'm a doctor because I want to
be accountable for what I do.

01:45:54.750 --> 01:45:56.268 line:85% position:50% size:80%
And to do it myself.

01:46:01.750 --> 01:46:02.900 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Fucker.

01:47:47.500 --> 01:47:48.641 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Hello?

01:47:49.667 --> 01:47:51.146 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Good evening, sir.

01:47:52.332 --> 01:47:53.664 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Don't worry about it.

01:47:55.167 --> 01:47:56.543 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Of course, no problem.

01:47:58.582 --> 01:48:01.625 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Train station? I'll be right there.

01:48:21.125 --> 01:48:24.289 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
Thank you for coming.
I know it's late.

01:48:24.375 --> 01:48:25.582 line:85% position:50% size:80%
No problem, sir.

01:48:25.667 --> 01:48:28.119 line:85% position:50% size:80%
I want to ask a personal favor.

01:48:29.125 --> 01:48:31.520 line:85% position:50% size:80%
You know my son got arrested.

01:48:33.042 --> 01:48:36.769 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
I'm going to Warsaw...
Anyway...

01:48:39.457 --> 01:48:43.603 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
You see, I was to go
to Libya in about a month.

01:48:44.750 --> 01:48:46.497 line:85% position:50% size:80%
But now they won't let me.

01:48:46.582 --> 01:48:49.574 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
- He went away for distributing leaflets?
- Yes.

01:48:49.750 --> 01:48:52.332 line:85% position:50% size:80%
I didn't sign the protest letter.

01:48:52.542 --> 01:48:55.556 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
I know. Back then
I thought you were right.

01:48:58.332 --> 01:48:59.886 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Now I'm not so sure.

01:49:01.125 --> 01:49:03.832 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
I couldn't.
I want to be impartial.

01:49:03.917 --> 01:49:08.109 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
You're a decent man,
that's all that really matters.

01:49:10.167 --> 01:49:13.713 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
I came to ask you
to replace me on that trip.

01:49:15.292 --> 01:49:19.713 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
You know my methods. It's just
a few consultations and lectures.

01:49:19.957 --> 01:49:21.787 line:85% position:50% size:80%
I have them written down.

01:49:24.082 --> 01:49:26.949 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
- No need to answer today.
- I'll go, no problem.

01:49:27.332 --> 01:49:30.822 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
Hear me out before
you say yes.

01:49:31.832 --> 01:49:35.712 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
I can't think of anyone else
willing to help me out.

01:49:36.917 --> 01:49:39.253 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
I probably won't be
Dean much longer.

01:49:39.692 --> 01:49:42.326 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
They'll probably remove me
from the Academy altogether.

01:49:42.411 --> 01:49:45.332 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
I think they'll let you out
of the country

01:49:45.417 --> 01:49:49.636 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
but bear in mind it may be
your last trip for years to come.

01:49:50.750 --> 01:49:53.829 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
I wanted you to know that
and to think about it.

01:49:55.625 --> 01:49:58.872 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
If you decide to go,
call me.

01:49:59.917 --> 01:50:02.927 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Otherwise just forget we met.

01:50:10.625 --> 01:50:13.090 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
Sir, I've decided.
I'll go.

01:50:23.250 --> 01:50:27.164 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
It happens to be
my wife's birthday

01:50:27.250 --> 01:50:31.667 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
- so I'd like to reschedule if possible.
- I'll see what can be done.

01:50:32.250 --> 01:50:33.604 line:85% position:50% size:80%
I love her so much.

01:50:35.917 --> 01:50:39.278 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
There is a flight on the 11th,
via Paris.

01:50:39.750 --> 01:50:43.380 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
It's a foreign airline,
I'll check if you can fly with them.

01:50:51.582 --> 01:50:52.993 line:85% position:50% size:80%
I like your lighter.

01:50:53.582 --> 01:50:57.091 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
Your ticket was purchased abroad
so there's no problem.

01:50:57.792 --> 01:51:03.038 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
I'll check seat availability,
then change your ticket.

01:51:04.125 --> 01:51:06.747 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
- When can I come back?
- In a couple of days.

01:51:06.832 --> 01:51:07.679 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Great.

01:51:27.207 --> 01:51:28.606 line:85% position:50% size:80%
We're cleaning up?

01:51:29.750 --> 01:51:31.000 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Go to bed.

01:51:31.582 --> 01:51:34.099 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
I'll empty the ashtrays
and tidy up a bit.

01:51:50.457 --> 01:51:53.257 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
Will you see me off to Warsaw?
To the airport?

01:51:54.082 --> 01:51:55.694 line:85% position:50% size:80%
You know I'm on call.

01:51:59.375 --> 01:52:02.076 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
- Don't go.
- You mean it?

01:52:03.875 --> 01:52:06.150 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
- No.
- My mind's made up.

01:52:06.375 --> 01:52:07.512 line:85% position:50% size:80%
I want to go.

01:52:13.667 --> 01:52:15.896 line:85% position:50% size:80%
I was watching you one night...

01:52:18.042 --> 01:52:19.149 line:85% position:50% size:80%
And?

01:52:20.114 --> 01:52:21.310 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Nothing.

01:52:49.850 --> 01:52:52.644 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
Write to tell me what you thought
when you heard this.

01:52:52.729 --> 01:52:53.747 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Heard what?

01:52:53.889 --> 01:52:55.832 line:85% position:50% size:80%
We're going to have a daughter.

01:52:56.792 --> 01:52:57.957 line:85% position:50% size:80%
A daughter?

01:53:29.417 --> 01:53:31.568 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
- Do you have a light?
- Sure.

01:53:35.207 --> 01:53:36.367 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Thank you.

01:53:44.582 --> 01:53:48.618 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
